#. <section class="sutta" id="an9.52"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an9.52:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 9"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 9"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an9.52:0.2"
msgid "6. Khemavagga"
msgstr "6. A Safe Place"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an9.52:0.3"
msgid "52. Khemasutta"
msgstr "52. A Safe Place"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an9.52:1.1"
msgid "“‘Khemaṃ, kheman’ti, āvuso, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend, they speak of ‘a safe place’."

msgctxt "an9.52:1.2"
msgid "Kittāvatā nu kho, āvuso, khemaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā”ti?"
msgstr "In what way did the Buddha speak of a safe place?”"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an9.52:2.1"
msgid ""
"“Idhāvuso, bhikkhu vivicceva kāmehi … pe … paṭhamaṃ jhānaṃ upasampajja "
"viharati."
msgstr ""
"“First, take a mendicant who, quite secluded from sensual pleasures … enters "
"and remains in the first absorption."

msgctxt "an9.52:2.2"
msgid "Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, khemaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā pariyāyena … pe …."
msgstr "To this extent the Buddha spoke of a safe place in a qualified sense. …"

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an9.52:3.1"
msgid ""
"Puna caparaṃ, āvuso, bhikkhu sabbaso nevasaññānāsaññāyatanaṃ samatikkamma "
"saññāvedayitanirodhaṃ upasampajja viharati, paññāya cassa disvā āsavā "
"parikkhīṇā honti."
msgstr ""
"Furthermore, take a mendicant who, going totally beyond the dimension of "
"neither perception nor non-perception, enters and remains in the cessation "
"of perception and feeling. And, having seen with wisdom, their defilements "
"come to an end."

msgctxt "an9.52:3.2"
msgid "Ettāvatāpi kho, āvuso, khemaṃ vuttaṃ bhagavatā nippariyāyenā”ti."
msgstr ""
"To this extent the Buddha spoke of a safe place in an unqualified sense.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an9.52:3.3"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ."
msgstr ""
